cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. The use of LSTM models also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves classification tasks, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
